name: THE COMPLETE SELFISH SERIES
description: All 6 previously released Selfish Levels in one episode plus a new final map. All of the original levels have been vastly improved with better lighting effects and much improved texture alignment. So relive the entire selfish series, 7 levels of pure Doom2 evilness at its very best. This wad has been released to dedicate my 10 years of Doom Level designing.
